thread.title: BRIEF-Docusign Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $100 Million

title: BRIEF-Docusign Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $100 Million
text:
March 28, 2018 / 8:35 PM / Updated 5 minutes ago BRIEF-Docusign Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $100 Million Reuters Staff 
March 28 (Reuters) - Docusign Inc : 
* DOCUSIGN INC FILES FOR IPO OF UP TO $100 MILLION – SEC FILING 
* DOCUSIGN INC SAYS IT INTENDS TO APPLY TO HAVE ITS COMMON STOCK LISTED ON NASDAQ GLOBAL SELECT MARKET UNDER THE SYMBOL “DOCU” 
* DOCUSIGN INC SAYS MORGAN STANLEY, J.P. MORGAN, CITIGROUP ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO 
* DOCUSIGN INC SAYS BOFA MERRILL LYNCH, DEUTSCHE BANK SECURITIES, JMP SECURITIES ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO 
* DOCUSIGN INC SAYS PIPER JAFFRAY, WILLIAM BLAIR ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO 
* DOCUSIGN INC SAYS PROPOSED IPO PRICE IS AN ESTIMATE SOLELY FOR CALCULATING SEC REGISTRATION FEE Source text : ( bit.ly/2GgYZxC )
